These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, cat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Pet   | goldfish | cat | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, old-henry, baccarat
1. the swisher-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##2
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Cigar   | baccarat | swisher | old-henry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
