1. the davidoff-smoker is between the ritmeester-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##2
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | davidoff | ritmeester |

