.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, may, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in february##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Birthday   | february | april | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, coach, freelancer
1. the analyst is between the freelancer and the coach##2
2. the freelancer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Job   | coach | analyst | freelancer |

